DID YOU KNOW → If we hadn’t passed the One Big Beautiful Bill, the American people were set to see a $4.3 TRILLION tax hike.

Not any more.

@SenateGOP and @POTUS are ensuring you keep more of your hard earned $$.

Enjoyed the chance to raise a few issues with @SecDuffy today – We particularly discussed the dire need to modernize our air traffic control system.
@POTUS’ vision to overhaul and revitalize our ATC system is welcome news for the flying public. 

I emphasized the importance of our smaller airports in the overall system and vowed to work with him to make sure airports in West Virginia will be eligible for vital federal funding.

Great news! Billy Marshall has done great things as Commissioner of the WV Division of Corrections and Rehabilitation, and I know that he will do even better things as the Director of the @OfficialFBOP! 

@POTUS picked the perfect candidate.

Congratulations, Director Marshall!

The Senate’s budget resolution paves the way for @POTUS’ historic tax cuts to be made permanent.

@SenateGOP is determined to help you keep more of your hard earned paycheck.
